  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Related SKS and LG-family pages</h2>
    <ul class="related-links">
      <li><a href="/brands/signature-kitchen-suite/">Signature Kitchen Suite brand hub →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/lg-stove-repair/">LG stove repair (mainstream parent) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/wolf-stove-repair/">Wolf stove repair →</a></li>
